# Quake Live server access list — the server's own admin / mod / ban list,
# referenced by g_accessFile in ffa/server.cfg. This is separate from minqlx
# permissions (those live in Redis and use qlx_owner / !admin / !mod).
#
# Copy this file to access.txt and add your own entries.
# Run reload_access if editing while the server is running; the server may also
# rewrite this file on map exit / shutdown.
#
# 1 entry per line, format: steamid|(mod|admin|ban)
# ex: 76561198072786081|ban
00000000000000000|admin
